{"tid":2449654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警犬咬傷油麻地六旬婦 右腳受傷送院","createTime":"2021-03-17T00:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T04:10:19.000Z","uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eadbbd922798fe47114fae2c2d5040b0c26f0353","tid":2449654,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:29:10.000Z","msg":"周一（15日）上午11時許，一名61歲女子在油麻地覺士道及佐敦道交界被一頭警犬咬傷，該名女子右腳受傷，清醒被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n該頭警犬為一頭雄性的德國狼犬，現正被隔離接受觀察。警犬隊正跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n德國狼犬即德國牧羊犬，警犬隊成立初期，一如外國的警犬隊是以德國牧羊犬為主。警隊網站稱，德國狼犬性格忠心、勇敢、兼外型威武，是警察在巡邏的最佳工作伙伴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210316/RZ3U76TTJNDQ5L6DWBSX7ZEWIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210316%2FRZ3U76TTJNDQ5L6DWBSX7ZEWIE%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=9f87fd8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210316%2FRZ3U76TTJNDQ5L6DWBSX7ZEWIE%2F&h=1f633bc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210316/RZ3U76TTJNDQ5L6DWBSX7ZEWIE/</a>"},{"pid":"58e9ea147f828d471d9953361bdb77e312495b60","tid":2449654,"uid":19712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:35:30.000Z","msg":"60歲婦襲擊警犬牙齒"},{"pid":"04b1ed2f9d9270218a62ed02eb59bbef0ad68b9b","tid":2449654,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:38:39.000Z","msg":"發情期係咁，仲要黑警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec9fc9a703f634291830538d1e6ff37014381c4","tid":2449654,"uid":189328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:08:32.000Z","msg":"我懷疑隻警犬命令隻警犬咬個阿嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57481c31aeb2a05f62e256fcd319cb7faa3c6e0e","tid":2449654,"uid":195893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:10:35.000Z","msg":"又襲警"},{"pid":"4b3a7317fe9cb082470d933339ec905dfa3f7a07","tid":244